data.meta_description: Index to Deaths 1870-1923 in Sherburne County, Minnesota
data.text:
Deaths 1870 - 1923

Deaths recorded in Sherburne county for the years 1870 to 1923 are extracted from death registers held by the county recorder's office. Books A, B, C, and E are indexes, and Book D contains death certificates.

This list is arranged first by the book in which it is recorded, then alphabetically by surname. It includes the date of death, the location of death- usually the township in the county, the age at death, and the birthplace. The age at death is given in years, months and days, and can be used to extrapolate the birth date.

The information recorded in the death registers A, B, C, D and E are slightly different. The registers include this information:
